title: The Adventures of Jason and the Argonauts (2015) PC [FINAL]

============================================
The Adventures of Jason and the Argonauts (2015) PC [FINAL]
============================================

- ENG

============================================
Description:                               =
============================================

Take a journey back to the times of Gods and Heroes. Follow Jason through his exciting adventures by playing Match 3 levels. Play a variety of meta game levels to make yourself a part of the myth. Take a challenge in three modes of difficulty. Win the favor of Gods and use their patronage to make your path safe. Collect hero gear and build an ancient city. Find pieces of the map that will lead you to your next destination..

============================================
FEATURES:                                  =
============================================

-Diversity of puzzles in every chapter
-Swap, group and chain Match 3 levels
-Choose one of 3 modes of difficulty
